35:36.220 --> 35:40.247
That sure doesn't look like what we asked for.
Where's the list ofWesten's known associates?

35:40.324 --> 35:43.088
How about the photos? How about the inventory
ofwhat he's got in that apartment?

35:43.160 --> 35:46.459
No, no. That's much better.
That's Alvaro Desantos. Good stuff.

35:46.530 --> 35:48.998
- Is he involved with Westen?
- Mmm, no.

35:49.066 --> 35:53.127
That's just something I picked up
poking around. Kind of a side project.

35:53.203 --> 35:55.433
The hell you want us
to do with it?

35:55.506 --> 36:00.375
Onlywhatyou boys are legally bound to, which is
take it from me, log it and pass it upstairs.

36:00.444 --> 36:04.380
It's gotta be worth at least a couple thou
in reward money, right?

36:04.448 --> 36:08.646
[ Chuckles ]
Man, I'm just about ready for dessert.

36:20.564 --> 36:23.465
I suppose I should thankyou
for not blowing out my tires again.

36:23.534 --> 36:26.196
You know, Gellman,
you're a better guy than I thought.

36:26.270 --> 36:29.171
I betyou gotyour daughter
that pony after all.

36:29.239 --> 36:31.969
- What the hell areyou talking about?
- Thankyou.

36:32.042 --> 36:33.976
Talking your client
into flipping on the big boys.

36:34.044 --> 36:37.104
Assault chargegets kicked,
mywitness is offthe hook.

36:37.181 --> 36:39.911
Win-win.

36:39.983 --> 36:42.645
I get it.
You don't discuss client business.

36:42.719 --> 36:45.916
J ust know I appreciate it.
I really do.

36:48.225 --> 36:51.388
[ Air Hissing ]

36:51.461 --> 36:54.487
That's for trying to kill me.

36:55.799 --> 36:57.266
[ Beeping]

36:57.334 --> 36:59.427
- [ Sam ] He go for it, Mike?
- Yeah.

36:59.503 --> 37:03.906
He's gonna be on the phone with whatever
F.B.I. contacts he's got before his tire goes flat.

37:03.974 --> 37:06.568
My guess is he'll have
the tape by lunch.

37:06.643 --> 37:09.077
We'll see how the big boys
in Colombia like that.

37:09.146 --> 37:11.341
[Michael Narrating]
A drug cartel is a business.

37:11.415 --> 37:14.509
Ifkilling a witness to protect
a valued employee from jail time...

37:14.585 --> 37:18.419
is the best way to keep making money,
they'll do that.

37:18.488 --> 37:22.549
If it looks like that employee is
testify.ing to the F..B.I., though...

37:22.626 --> 37:27.359
they're just as happy to leave the witness alone
and take care ofthe problem another way.

37:36.673 --> 37:40.973
I hear you're thi nki ng about taking a trip,
going out of town.

37:41.044 --> 37:43.604
What?
Who told you that?

37:43.680 --> 37:47.013
I've got some friends with the F.B.I.

37:47.084 --> 37:49.644
The F.B.I.?

37:52.089 --> 37:54.455
What the--

37:56.426 --> 38:00.385
No! It's not true. No.

38:06.103 --> 38:09.163
Shame... to let them
have all the fun.

38:09.239 --> 38:11.935
I'm just glad it's done.

38:14.911 --> 38:18.312
Do I get to have my key now?

38:47.711 --> 38:50.737
[Madeline ]
Michael! You have people here.

38:56.420 --> 38:58.445
Yourmothergave it to me.

39:00.090 --> 39:02.490
She's nice.

39:02.559 --> 39:06.552
I went byyour house, and Fiona told me
you were here. I hope that's okay.

39:06.630 --> 39:09.463
- That's fine.
- Well, we just wanted to say thankyou.

39:10.701 --> 39:13.568
In person.
Also, I could payyou.

39:13.637 --> 39:17.266
- You know, when I get my check--
- Don't worry about it.
Oleg has been more than generous.

39:17.341 --> 39:20.367
- But--
- No, seriously.

39:21.611 --> 39:24.580
- Cool car.
- We'll see if it works.

39:24.648 --> 39:26.582
[ Engine Starts ]

39:26.650 --> 39:28.982
Hey, what do you know?

39:30.520 --> 39:33.148
- [ Engine Shuts Off]
- Your mom said this was your dad's car.

39:33.223 --> 39:35.157
Sounds like he was a pretty cool guy.

39:35.225 --> 39:38.592
Not really.
I left home for a reason.

39:38.662 --> 39:41.256
Well, I'm glad that I didn't have to.

39:55.679 --> 39:57.840
"Beloved" is a bit ofa stretch.

40:14.531 --> 40:17.056
Thanks for the car, Dad.

40:17.134 --> 40:19.534
I thinkyou'dlike howit looks.

40:23.807 --> 40:26.537
- We meet here?
- You wanted someplace safe.

40:26.610 --> 40:31.013
It's quiet, lots of cover. Two guys in
business suits don't raise any eyebrows.

40:31.081 --> 40:33.675
You should have more meetings outside, Thabet.
Get some color.

40:33.750 --> 40:37.049
You were always good, Michael.
It's a shameyou're out.

40:37.120 --> 40:39.520
I'm gonna get back in.

40:41.892 --> 40:44.656
I've enjoyed our friendship.
But--

40:44.728 --> 40:47.561
But don't call you ever again.
I got it.

40:51.067 --> 40:53.126
Michael.

40:55.071 --> 40:57.335
Be careful.

